high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the plant on the ground under the window.
Pick up the white watering can on the ground to the left of the plant.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn left again and walk across the room to the wall, then turn left and walk up to the small white table in the corner of the room.
Turn on the light of the small lamp on the small white table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Examine a watering can in the light of a small lamp.

high_descs: Move across the room to the window facing the floor with the white curtains
Pick up the tea pot sitting on the floor below the window
Carry the tea pot to the round white table with the lamp on top of it
anns.task_desc: Carry the tea pot white turning on a lamp

high_descs: Move forward then turn right head in front of the plant
Pick up the watering can on the floor beside the plant
Turn to your left, cross the room and head to the lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine the watering can by the light
